    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting. so you're saying it's pretty much a consensus that the benefits are the main cause? i've seen some people arguing that stuff like automation or just changing demographics plays a bigger role though. don't you think those factors are just as important to look at?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
